sentences:
The sky is clear; the stars are 
twinkling.

The concept of 'first' seems to 
problematically be centered 
around patriarchy.

The quick brown fox jumps over 
the lazy dog.

In my dream, everyone was a 
pony and we all ate rainbows 
and pooped butterflies.

If your canoe is stuck in a 
tree with the headlights on, 
how many pancakes does it take 
to get to the moon?

The newest hero in Overwatch is 
a mech-driving hamster called 
Hammond.

It's a common misconception 
that D.Va was a pro Starcraft 
player.
